should suffice.

263
00:19:31,003 --> 00:19:32,963
- Is he still looking at me funny?
- Yes, he is.

264
00:19:33,047 --> 00:19:34,757
Tell him to stop
or I'll pull up his search history.

265
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:36,550
If you don't stop looking at the doctor,

266
00:19:36,634 --> 00:19:38,302
-he'll take a closer look--
