267
00:19:38,386 --> 00:19:40,346
And tell him his men report to me now.

268
00:19:41,472 --> 00:19:44,141
Excuse me? Listen, pal,
I don't know if you realize--

269
00:19:44,225 --> 00:19:46,060
I'm sorry, Major. What was your name?

270
00:19:46,143 --> 00:19:47,812
-Benning--
-Nobody cares!

271
00:19:48,771 --> 00:19:52,274
Nobody cares. Listen, Major Nobody Cares.

272
00:19:52,358 --> 00:19:54,652
You know why nobody cares who you are?

273
00:19:54,735 --> 00:19:57,113
Because nobody cares
about your feeble accomplishments.

274
00:19:57,196 --> 00:20:00,074
