277
00:20:07,373 --> 00:20:09,417
But she leaves a big creepy egg sac.

278
00:20:12,294 --> 00:20:14,004
My babies.

279
00:20:14,839 --> 00:20:17,091
Look what came out of my egg sac.

280
00:20:17,174 --> 00:20:19,260
You know what I love about machines?

281
00:20:20,344 --> 00:20:23,556
