and put the boat in the water.

283
00:20:27,727 --> 00:20:29,562
Now you do what you're told.

284
00:20:29,645 --> 00:20:32,356
Stand over there on the edge
of your personal abyss...

285
00:20:33,357 --> 00:20:35,443
and watch my machines do your job.

286
00:20:38,195 --> 00:20:40,656
- Can you feel it, Stone?
- I can feel it, Doctor.

287
00:20:41,323 --> 00:20:42,825
It's evolution, Stone.

288
00:20:44,034 --> 00:20:45,369
It's evolution!

289
00:21:21,405 --> 00:21:23,532
- Agent Stone?
- Doctor.

290
00:21:23,616 --> 00:21:25,534
Do you see anything useful in this image?

291
00:21:26,786 --> 00:21:29,538
- Nothing at ail, Doctor.
- Of course you don't.

292
00:21:29,622 --> 00:21:31,499
Your eyes weren't
expertly trained to spot tracks

293
00:21:31,582 --> 00:21:34,168
by the Native American Shadow Wolves.

